name: Cowboy Love is Pure 1-017: You Have Failed
description: Chapter 1, panel 17. The street outside is empty. A cowboy could use some helpful guidance. A centipede is always there to give it, if one is only to listen. The bricks creak as night cools the air. Dust is untrampled from the surface of the tarmac. A comic by Little Old Man. This panel is an edition of 30.
